      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here. It's ready for its next adventure, and I know you're going to love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
