    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen is mechanically pristine, with the critical rod bearing service recently completed using VAC coated shells and a comprehensive Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul. The chassis integrity is guaranteed by a proactive subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential with zero lash. The suspension geometry remains factory-perfect, providing the tactile feedback and lateral grip these M-cars are famed for. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its original depth and luster with no evidence of road rash or oxidation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
